{"tid":546532,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"JJ插沙 脫毒 Gel極都Gel唔起個頭","createTime":"2018-01-31T15:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T04:13:39.000Z","uid":55939,"like":6,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"05c20c159a2c7d9dcef62d45c2d91b894da9db1d","tid":546532,"uid":55939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:18:20.000Z","msg":"小弟想脫毒 跪求賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咁既<br />\n細佬我個頭點Gel都好<br />\n都Gel唔到all back個類頭<br />\n我既頭髮係好幼同埋好軟<br />\n<br />\nGel極都Gel唔起 唯有噴多幾野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但之後 硬過碌鳩 D頭髮變成一條條咁 好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係個形只係hold到1-2小時 之後又跌返落黎<br />\n<br />\n唔想一世都有個陰係到做MK仔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求高人指點<br />\n邊隻髮泥同Spray係岩我髮質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b1381fe14e60726566c68be08cdfb91cad3f99","tid":546532,"uid":21423,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:20:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b64c399c8745ff396fec47d3ece764cbdc30ca7","tid":546532,"uid":169468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:23:15.000Z","msg":"影個頭上嚟睇下"},{"pid":"082657fccea17545ff694e45c77bcb131c7d79d1","tid":546532,"uid":24989,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:23:27.000Z","msg":"謝霆鋒.gif"},{"pid":"951bdfc8b518d2ba21244e51a7c330b07500cc79","tid":546532,"uid":59830,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:25:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3cbbd68b7d52520374e0dfed